rows.label: tev061301_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Popo why she is here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Popo if anything is troubling her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0001
rows.name:
Is friend sightseeing too? This place so pure and white
and mystical as far as eye can see![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0002
rows.name: Nothing at all like home of Popo in Cauldros![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0003
rows.name:
Popo would move here in heartbeat if Dadapon
allowed it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0004
rows.name: But that will never happen. Dadapon way too strict.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0005
rows.name:
Oh well! All that really matter is Popo enjoying special
time with beloved Nio.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0008
rows.name:
Nio been stealing glances at shop over there this
whole time...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0009
rows.name: Popo hope he not planning to buy anything funny.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0010
rows.name: Like...one of those pollen orbs...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0011
rows.name:
No, Nio never do that. Nio not that kind of Nopon!
Popo just worry too much because of love for Nio.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Popo about her dress.

rows.label: tev061301_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Popo about recent developments.

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0012
rows.name:
Popo put away pure white dress given by Nio in order
to keep it safe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0013
rows.name:
Popo and Nio promise to save up enough money for
wedding first. Time for dress will come![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0014
rows.name:
Right now Popo need to tighten purse strings.
No more wasteful spending![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0015
rows.name:
Popo not need rich and extravagant life of movie star.
Credit saved is credit earned![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0019
rows.name:
Popo has made up mind and decided not to return
home to Dadapon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0020
rows.name:
Instead, Popo will marry Nio and live right here
in Sylvalum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0021
rows.name:
Popo not want Nio to go through trouble just because
family of Popo have money.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0022
rows.name:
Popo would rather just say good-bye to money!
Time for clean slate on new continent.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0023
rows.name:
And Popo have friend to thank for helping Popo arrive
at this bold decision.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061301_MSG0024
rows.name:
Thanks, [ST:playername ]! If friend had not
started hullabaloo over ring, Popo might have been
mired in indecision for all time.[ST:wait ]
